@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About NATS Shop</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1>About NATS Shop</h1>
    
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h2>Project Overview</h2>
            <p>
                NATS Shop is a demonstration of a modern microservice-based e-commerce application built with .NET 9.0.
                It showcases how to build scalable, resilient, and maintainable web applications using a microservice architecture.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Microservice Architecture</strong> - Separate services for products, with clear boundaries and responsibilities</li>
                <li><strong>NATS Messaging</strong> - Using NATS as a lightweight, high-performance messaging system for service communication</li>
                <li><strong>Request/Reply Pattern</strong> - Implementing synchronous communication between services</li>
                <li><strong>PostgreSQL Database</strong> - Storing product and inventory data in a relational database</li>
                <li><strong>Entity Framework Core</strong> - Using EF Core for database access and migrations</li>
                <li><strong>Blazor WebAssembly Frontend</strong> - Modern, component-based UI running in the browser</li>
                <li><strong>Docker Containerization</strong> - Packaging the application for consistent deployment</li>
                <li><strong>Health Monitoring</strong> - Implementing health checks for services</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">Architecture</h3>
            <p>
                The application follows a microservice architecture with the following components:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Frontend</strong> - Blazor WebAssembly application that provides the user interface</li>
                <li><strong>API Gateway</strong> - Entry point for all client requests, routing them to appropriate services</li>
                <li><strong>Products Service</strong> - Manages product data and inventory</li>
                <li><strong>NATS Server</strong> - Message broker for service communication</li>
                <li><strong>PostgreSQL Database</strong> - Persistent storage for product data</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">Technologies Used</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>.NET 9.0</li>
                <li>ASP.NET Core</li>
                <li>Blazor WebAssembly</li>
                <li>Entity Framework Core</li>
                <li>NATS</li>
                <li>PostgreSQL</li>
                <li>Docker</li>
                <li>Bootstrap 5</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h4 class="mb-0">Project Information</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p><strong>Version:</strong> 1.0.0</p>
                    <p><strong>Framework:</strong> .NET 9.0</p>
                    <p><strong>Frontend:</strong> Blazor WebAssembly</p>
                    <p><strong>Backend:</strong> ASP.NET Core Microservices</p>
                    <p><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL</p>
                    <p><strong>Messaging:</strong> NATS</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
